doc.after: Boeing Launch Services Inc BLS is Boeing s commercial launch service provider On behalf of its commercial customers BLS administers launch service contracts for Delta II and Delta IV launches conducted by United Launch Alliance In November 2010 Boeing Defense Space Security was selected by NASA for consideration for potential contract awards for heavy lift launch vehicle system concepts and propulsion technologies 11
